{"tid":1472518,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"趕鬼，不捉鬼！","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T15:10:40.000Z","uid":307385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"293de3383bb09ed02564cf8c149d558bc546a7a6","tid":1472518,"uid":307385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"代耶撚frd發:<br />\n昨天的經驗改良如下，希望下次用得著：<br />\n1. 搵到鬼，當然唔好咁輕易放過佢啦。以牙還牙、以眼還眼；錫佢春袋定踢佢春袋；或者拍照多謝對方深明大義支持香港抗爭發放到微信、微博，前線手足自行決定。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 重重之重，捉到鬼，其實係唔想佢招來更多鬼，無論是外鬼（黑警藉口驅散）定內鬼（事後分化手足），因此，捉到鬼手足可以留意四周出入口，同時設置路障佈防，制定（較為）安全距離。希望咁做可以拉遠同黑警戰線。</span></span></strong><br />\n3. 放定唔放，前提還是尊重前線。既然已有2嘅防線設咗，爭取時間同空間以鬼質作為籌碼交涉，如果最後選擇放嘅，一定一定一定唔該搵埋記者同勇武手足跟埋去，手足有車義載就最好，唔好只係俾黑警護航，不過人數比例方面為4手足 比2警察（喂，你有裝架），按情況而定，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">條件不達成，不放人！</span></span></strong><br />\n唔知work 唔work，不過重點係，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">趕鬼而不招鬼。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n耶穌咁趕鬼<br />\n趕鬼在於清潔自己的心思，這樣鬼才不會再搞擾你。<br />\n（昨日反思，沒錯好憤怒，但憤怒的力量可以善用，具強大力量，但要以心制怒（不怒也者，心不為憤之奴）。心思定而則能於亂而謀後路。）<br />\n//「污鬼離了人身，就在無水之地過來過去，尋求安歇 之處 ；既尋不着，便說：『我要回到我所出來的屋裏去。』 到了，就看見 裏面 打掃乾淨，修飾好了， 便去<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">另帶了七個比自己更惡的鬼來，都進去住在那裏。那人末後的景況比先前更不好了。</span></ins></strong>」//<br />\n路加福音 11:24‭-‬26"},{"pid":"6855a39b1b658df76b32fe5598c44fbe20aa3be4","tid":1472518,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZTgDYpe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZTgDYpe.jpg&h=7e43d75b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzNop4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzNop4e.jpg&h=0d3d92d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a92cdd99835ea1246a5893cfebd1d23e2bc750fb","tid":1472518,"uid":307385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:09:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bab1e0446c705ea5715f8ea933f9d993d308eb","tid":1472518,"uid":307385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"040e2a6708d69d775018dd4cedda333899e19953","tid":1472518,"uid":307385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af362cdfb5f5e5542d3e61b87295b95e53916a17","tid":1472518,"uid":307385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e448a6c950c5116476da5273b1a9bbefeebfcc13","tid":1472518,"uid":307385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:09:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4170660d5ec91bb3f52acc8a1132027973c17fd7","tid":1472518,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n長期戰 不氣餒</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>8月15日</strong>：稅局接收工（1200稅務大樓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月16日</strong>：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月17日</strong>：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月18日</strong>：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月24日</strong>：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>8月25日</strong>：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位手足，到時見！</span></strong>"},{"pid"